data.description: New to market in the heart of Roseville is this turnkey, newly remodeled home with seemingly endless upgrades! The remodel includes a new fifty-year Presidential comp shingle roof, new Mission interior doors, trim, & crown molding, baseboards, and fresh interior paint. Also installed is Karastan Premium wool carpet with waterproof thick padding in the Great Room and Master Bedroom. The Master Bedroom is enhanced with mirrored closet doors and custom frosted glass. Enjoy grilling in your secluded backyard and cool off swimming on a hot summer day in your large in-ground pool upgraded energy-efficient pool pump. Enjoy beautiful sunsets under your new custom covered patio with lighting and ceiling fan, protected with a 7-foot high redwood stained fence for full privacy! Stay cool inside with a completely new HVAC system and new ducting. Additionally, the air-handler was moved from the kitchen to the attic to create a new lighted pantry with custom wood shelves. Stay warm on cold nights with a NEW Blaze King Catalytic converter wood burning stove. You're walking distance to Old Town Roseville, Diamond Oaks Park, or Lincoln Estates Park.  Take a quick drive to Roseville Galleria or any number of family restaurants. See this home today!
